{"tid":1380777,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[訴求上級] 警隊惡行已經唔係成立獨立調查委員會就夠","createTime":"2019-07-29T05:54:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T06:16:51.000Z","uid":161430,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b48a0a0ba98ae9139b5902d2afb6feeec65a4229","tid":1380777,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:54:42.000Z","msg":"一，<br />\n首先應該講，獨立調查委員會有用，等如普選都有用，<br />\n但問題係，你確保到係<span style=\"color: red;\">真</span>獨立調查委員會咩，<br />\n<br />\n正如香港人以前追求普選時已經比人呃過一次，<br />\n所以先會叫「我要<span style=\"color: red;\">真普選</span>」，<br />\n其實我唔明，點解今日香港人又會返返去叫要獨立調查委員會 就足夠既程度？<br />\n<br />\n二，<br />\n其實<span style=\"color: red;\">警察惡行已經遠遠唔止要獨立調查委員會</span>，<br />\n最少我覺得，宜家已經可以開始叫定「我要真獨立調查委員會」<br />\n而且係要<span style=\"color: red;\">先解散成個警隊，等佢地冇得撈，再要佢地受調查</span><br />\n<br />\n如果唔係將來發現委員會係假野既時候，又後悔多次<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n試着叫<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">解散警隊<br />\n成立真獨立調查委員會</span></span>"},{"pid":"e2e74e9c6d36b4fac2f364dae1d78a874d889494","tid":1380777,"uid":997,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:55:10.000Z","msg":"直頭要開軍事法庭"},{"pid":"11b7ef91f9c90a71e8ee840e6d098125b97bef80","tid":1380777,"uid":161430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:56:03.000Z","msg":"請將行動升級成罷工<br />\n訴求升級成解散警隊 + 真獨立調查委員會"},{"pid":"0ec10cb12b953f96d08162a59ed4d39b6c554487","tid":1380777,"uid":224075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:56:15.000Z","msg":"解散警隊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc2f8f816c57e1e966e48279f5effaf10a321f2","tid":1380777,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:56:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推! 8月5罷工!!!!! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日(7月29)1500-1830</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;